msg":"如果你本身無公司醫療 我建議你買個basic 醫療 plan 再on top 加一個有自負額既high end 醫療咁樣加埋可以用最少既錢拎到最大既保障<br />\n<br />\n我當你90出世 今年29歲計<br />\n一個有$22800自負額既high end 醫療 一個月$450左右 已經可以提供一年1200萬既醫療保障額 終身有3600萬 基本上有咩事去埋外國醫都唔洗擔心<br />\n<br />\n而你無公司醫療既情況下 我建議你買多個最basic 既醫療C plan 一個月$170 左右 for 反一d常見既小手術 姐係claim 埋開頭果$22800 <br />\n<br />\n咁2樣加埋 都係$620 左右 你已經每年有1200 萬既醫療保額  剩底先再諗埋需唔需要加危疾 for 反萬一有大型疾病有2-3 年反唔到工既生活費 我覺得咁係最理想 <br />\n<br />\n有野想問多d可tg<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/lam112100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flam112100&d=wuRAGhAhlQknfzdK5YHn80%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=fd854dbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lam112100</a>"},{"pid":"236d587e64033613e8217b1129b839f22f3d291f","tid":998782,"uid":25133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:17:18.000Z","msg":"有能力一定係睇私家<br />\n可以揀有少少墊底費既高端醫療<br />\n甚至乎你個budget已經可以揀無墊底費既"},{"pid":"2b335b62a2c384d4644094bbd6d54a9e1cbab6e6","tid":998782,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"878fdbac9b063dba91c10d7b9032f4fd73a5e684","tid":998782,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c132d17f7ca819886ff6e68116edcb8ded99db","tid":998782,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:42:16.000Z","msg":"買完，出事，呢樣唔包，果樣唔保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"跟錯保險公司好易奶野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:08:34.000Z","msg":"大病係咪claim過一次之後，就唔再保果種病？"},{"pid":"8e81ba8e4e7cf7e611afd20fab59b8c764858a65","tid":998782,"uid":53019,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:31:55.000Z","msg":"去東南亞醫，台灣唔錯！平一大截！"},{"pid":"b2f005906d6db18d3d6e5b8d7da356000d4219e9","tid":998782,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e81ba8e4e7cf7e611afd20fab59b8c764858a65","tid":998782,"uid":53019,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:31:55.000Z","msg":"去東南